WEBVTT

00:00:01.110 --> 00:00:05.429
How many people here have heard of PMS?

00:00:05.429 --> 00:00:06.915
Everybody, right?

00:00:06.915 --> 00:00:09.399
Everyone knows that women
go a little crazy

00:00:09.399 --> 00:00:12.270
right before they get their period,

00:00:12.270 --> 00:00:16.458
that the menstrual cycle throws them
onto an inevitable hormonal roller coaster

00:00:16.458 --> 00:00:19.151
of irrationality and irritability.

00:00:19.151 --> 00:00:20.939
There's a general assumption


00:00:20.939 --> 00:00:25.858
that fluctuations in reproductive hormones
cause extreme emotions

00:00:25.858 --> 00:00:29.391
and that the great majority of women
are affected by this.

